Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在传说终年冰雪不化的地方 斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆他们遇到了班图族的少女敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:02:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是班图族似乎被伊鲁贝克率领的 鬼骑士军团控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 巴隆在和伊鲁贝克的战斗中受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落山谷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯他们也被驱使到洞窟里干活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在雪山中进行的可怕阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的核心竟是能治愈受重伤的鬼骑士的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谜之花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:25.91,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,253)}激战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:25.91,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(343,388)}魔之山脊 -后篇-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆阁下 巴隆阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你恢复意识了吗 巴隆阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用高兴成这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到居然会在这种雪山重逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我偶然发现 你可能会就那样流着血被冻死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又受你关照了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 居然被奇怪的鬼手袭击落到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击你的恐怕是鬼骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是德罗斯特国的秘密军队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由从阿拉德大陆的各地 聚集而来的鬼剑士组成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说最近鬼骑士在斯顿雪域 似乎有图谋不轨的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是接到教团的命令而来这一带调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种偏僻的深山 那伙人到底想干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说鬼剑士们得到了产生鬼的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:05:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1 2 踩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我快点干 不然饶不了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那些混账
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要压榨我们到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这只手告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的鬼手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那是我来到军队之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是观光的古迹还是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能有这么大的功效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说我也很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样继续进行研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要用这种力量 改变大陆目前的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次得到的资料我这就送到本国的研究所去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被治愈的人 也马上送他们回国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族的家伙要怎么处置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的饭量可真是不容小觑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保守秘密 最好的办法就是灭口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就顺便把那个相亲相爱的Party也灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交给你们善后了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆阁下 你的伤还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心他们会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种性格还是没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有工夫舒服的躺着还不如起来干活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让他休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都在干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙该搬的东西还没搬完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就连他的份一起搬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 卡本西斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下你没什么好说的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽梅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面可真凉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再干下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 差不多该逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的体力 似乎也都到极限了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.71,0:08:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把班图族的人一起带出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡贝俏 你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 你们居然在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 我一打暗号你们就冲出箱子制造骚乱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去把我的武器拿回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 大家 一定要保护好老人和孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是要烧的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火力不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把下一个搬来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克爆弹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以尽情的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺负我的是哪个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族是自尊心很强的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会对鬼骑士卑颜屈膝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是族长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时候才更该统率大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那个世界后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救 救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 这花还有这样的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都没事就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧死你 啊热热热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.34,0:13:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么啊 那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 巴隆 还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 还好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也在 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这东西 在往上升啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 不能让它到地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西和白子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西到了地面上就会引起卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯 阻止它的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 把大家带到出口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不能失去那个花 别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前承蒙你关照了啊 要好好返还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 鬼手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.83,0:15:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个手和你的手不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说要让它停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 烧了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没有注意到这个事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 卡贝俏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖花 觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来和你玩玩 笨枪手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出口被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是纽梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚大人 从这走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把毫无关系的班图族也卷进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做大事多少都要有一些牺牲的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.98,0:17:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便决定别人的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想说的就这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽快结束战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你们都打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不是冲着你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙被打到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正是恶有恶报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见识到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做伊鲁贝克 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆·阿贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会记住这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是会很快就忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 倒大霉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:19:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.31,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都救出来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意 卡鲁松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚做的也很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那些家伙完全打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们借助那花的力量治好了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那力量是我们无法触碰的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片大陆至今还被诅咒着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那个卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,族人能得救全托你们的福 不胜感激
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们班图族也是勇敢的一族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.63,0:21:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结局圆满真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还在装什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 就算是我也不是不死之身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 人家可是一直在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子在担心我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.49,0:21:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵啦你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也差不多该告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你要去什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在来这的路上发现了一个很不错的温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想是不是要好好泡下保养下皮肤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们 在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.61,0:21:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对治愈伤口有好处的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去 要去 马上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我一个人的秘密哦 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:21:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:21:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啦 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们也没什么吧
